==English==

===Pronunciation===
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛɡeɪ|-ɛɡeɪ]]

===Noun===
'''reggae'''

# {{cattag|Music}} A form of music originating in [[Jamaica]] and associated with [[rastafarianism]], featuring a heavy base line, percussive rhythm guitar on the [[offbeat]], often with close vocal harmonies.

